fb_text2screen - opensource tool for simple text drawing on framebuffer devices.
http://git.slonopotamus.org/?p=fb_text2screen

Dependencies
------------
CMake >= 2.6 is required to build from sources.
popt is required at build and runtime for command-line args processing.

Compiling
---------
See the INSTALL document for build instructions.

Documentation
-------------
See --help output of fb_text2screen program.

